---

<section class="section memberships-s1">
  <div class="container--narrow memberships-s1__inner">
    <h1 class="memberships-s1__heading">Membership Plans</h1>

    <h3 class="memberships-s1__subheading">
      Enjoy the benefits of our Membership and enhance your beauty inside out.
    </h3>

    <p class="memberships-s1__body">
      Our Memberships offer you the choice to combine Menon Signature Facials with IV Vitamin
      Therapy at an incredible price! You can choose between a Monthly Subscription or a One Time
      Fee Package of 3 treatments.
    </p>

    <p class="memberships-s1__body">
      Interested to see what IV Drips are included in the Membership? Check out our IV Drip Menu.
    </p>

    <!-- Wix Membership pricing widget: replaced by external booking flow -->
    <div class="memberships-s1__booking-note">
      <p>
        Ready to become a member? Use the Members Booking Area to view plans and book your
        treatments.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="memberships-s1__ctas">
      <a href="/members-booking" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">
        Go To Member's Booking Area
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="btn btn--secondary btn--lg">
        Back to Home Page
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .memberships-s1__inner {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .memberships-s1__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .memberships-s1__subheading {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .memberships-s1__body {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .memberships-s1__booking-note {
    background-color: var(--color-tint);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    text-align: left;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .memberships-s1__booking-note p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .memberships-s1__ctas {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .memberships-s1__ctas {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .memberships-s1__ctas .btn {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 320px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .memberships-s1__booking-note {
      padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-sm);
    }
  }
</style>
